GravshipExport.ShipLayoutDefV2.label: Attack Ship
GravshipExport.ShipLayoutDefV2.description: Lock S-foils in attack position ! Get your raiding dreams started early, what she lacks in comfort and defensive capability she more than makes up for in firepower and range. Has a small bedroom, heaters and oxygen pumps, enough power for everything, a fuel optimiser, a pilot subcore and 4 auto cannon turrets, perfect for wrecking the day of any innocent tribal village on your first day.
